data.description: Exceptional opportunity to own a beautiful home nestled on Selah Loop Road with a truly enchanting living experience. The kitchen is fully updated, complete with newer appliances, ample counter space, and updated cabinetry. 3 bedrooms on the main level and 2 full baths. The primary serves as a private sanctuary with large walk-in closet, and access to the back deck. There is a non-conforming bedroom or additional space downstairs. The pasture is fully fenced with irrigation, ready for your animals. Additional features include a spacious garage, and modern amenities such as central heating and cooling. Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to own a piece of paradise on Selah Loop Road. Schedule a showing today & prepare to fall in love.
